snippet.title: Family Guy: Air Griffin
snippet.description:
Peter Griffin has just spent Meg's college fund on a freakin' sweet medieval catapult. Help him achieve greatness as he tries to smash the record for the world's longest unaided human flight. 
 
Launch Air Griffin now on your mobile phone! www.airgriffingame.com
